HEADWORD: Multivocal
<hw>Mul*tiv"o*cal</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Multi-</ets> + <ets>vocal</ets>.]</ety> <def>Signifying many
different things; of manifold meaning; equivocal.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧An
ambiguous <xex>multivocal</xex> word.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Coleridge.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>A multivocal word.</def>
